high_descs: Walk to the loaf of bread on the counter.
Grab the bread from the counter.
Walk to the fridge on your right.
Place the bread in the fridge, then take it out.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your left.
Place the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill bread and put it on a counter.

high_descs: Move to the right to face the bread on the counter.
Pick the bread up from off of the counter.
Turn around and then go to the right to face the refrigerator.
Place the bread inside of the refrigerator, wait a few seconds, and remove the bread from the refrigerator.
Turn to the left, go down to the end of the counter and turn right to face the sink.
Place the bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the refrigerated bread on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Go to the right a step, face the bread on the counter.
Take the bread from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn left to face the fridge, go to the fridge.
Chill the bread on the top shelf of the fridge. Take the bread from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, turn right to face the left side of the sink.
Put the bread on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on a counter.
